    "Multimodal AI": "Teaching AI to see, speak, and understand across text, images, video, and audio simultaneously.",
    "Generative Models": "The mathematics of creativity: diffusion models, image synthesis, and generative model architectures.",
    "Retrieval & Knowledge": "Augmenting language models with external knowledge through retrieval, adaptation, and grounding.",
    "Physical AI & Robotics": "Bridging the simulation-to-reality gap: physics engines, robot learning, and embodied intelligence.",
    "3D & Scene Understanding": "Representing and understanding 3D worlds — from neural radiance fields to graph-based spatial reasoning."
